otorclothes apparel and riding gear the company provides a range of services to its independent dealers including motorcycle service and business management training programs and customized dealer software packagesthe companys onroad motorcycle market comprises categories such as cruiser which emphasizes styling and owner customization touring which emphasizes rider comfort and load capacity and incorporates features such as fairings and luggage compartments standard which is a basic motorcycle that features upright seating for one or two passengers sportbike which incorporates racing technology aerodynamic styling low handlebars with a sport riding position and tires and dual which is designed with the capability for use on public roads as well as for some offhighway recreational use internationally the company operates facilities in brazil india and australiathe company serves a range of customers across multiple demographics both in the united states and across the world its motorcycles have engines with displacements that are greater than  cubic centimeters ccs up to a displacement of ccs the companys products are marketed to retail customers across the world primarily through digital and experiential activities as well as through traditional promotional and advertising activities the company operates the harleydavidson museum museum in milwaukee wisconsin as of december   the company distributed its motorcycles and related products to a network of independent dealers located in  countries across the worldfinancial services segmentthe financial services segment consists of hdfs which provides wholesale and retail financing and insurancerelated programs to the harleydavidson dealers and their retail customers hdfs is engaged in the business of financing and servicing wholesale inventory receivables and retail consumer loans for the purchase of harleydavidson motorcycles hdfs provides wholesale financial services to harleydavidson dealers including floorplan and open account financing of motorcycles and motorcycle parts and accessories hdfs offers wholesale financial services to harleydavidson dealers in the united states and canada hdfs operates as an agent for certain unaffiliated insurance companies offering pointofsale protection products through harleydavidson dealers in both the united states and canada including motorcycle insurance extended service contracts credit protection and motorcycle maintenance protectionhdfs directmarkets motorcycle insurance and extended service contracts to owners of harleydavidson motorcycles in addition hdfs markets a package of business insurance coverages and services to owners of harleydavidson dealerships internationally hdfs licenses the harleydavidson brand to local thirdparty financial institutions that offer products to the companys retail customers such as financing and insurance as of december   the financial services segment had three office facilities chicago illinois plano texas wholesale and retail operations and carson city nevada retail and insurance operations » full overview of hogn company address harleydavidson inc  w juneau avemilwaukee   wi    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation michael cave  matthew levatich  john olin  lawrence hund  tchernavia rocker  » more officers  directors harleydavidson inc news benetton family seeks to make ducati motorbikes italian sources jul   update us justice department drops  million harleydavidson emissions penalty jul   us justice department drops  million harleydavidson emissions penalty jul   us justice department drops m harleydavidson emissions penalty jul   justice department expected to drop  million harleydavidson emissions penalty sources jul   » more hogn news related topics stocksstock screenerauto  truck manufacturers dealer locator  harleydavidson usa skip to main content sign out online profile sign in shopping tools shopping tools compare bikes estimate payment build your harley sche