eydavidson emea harleydavidson brazil harleydavidson india harleydavidson asia website wwwharleydavidsoncom coordinates °′″n °′″w﻿  ﻿°n °w﻿    harleydavidson inc hd or harley is an american motorcycle manufacturer founded in milwaukee wisconsin in  as one of two major american motorcycle manufacturers to survive the great depression along with indian the company has survived numerous ownership arrangements subsidiary arrangements eg aermacchi  and buell  periods of poor economic health and product quality as well as intense global competition to become one of the worlds largest motorcycle manufacturers and an iconic brand widely known for its loyal following with owner clubs and events worldwide as well as a company sponsored brandfocused museum noted for a style of customization that gave rise to the chopper motorcycle style harleydavidson traditionally marketed heavyweight aircooled cruiser motorcycles with engine displacements greater than  cm³ and has broadened its offerings to include its more contemporary vrsc  and middleweight street  platforms harleydavidson manufactures its motorcycles at factories in york pennsylvania milwaukee wisconsin kansas city missouri manaus brazil and bawal india and markets its products worldwide besides motorcycles the company licenses and markets merchandise under the harleydavidson brand among them being apparel home decor and ornaments accessories toys and scale figures of its motorcycles and video games based on its motorcycle line and the community contents  history  beginning  world war i  bicycles  s  great depression  world war ii  small harleys hummers and aermacchis  overseas  tarnished reputation  restructuring and revival  buell motorcycle company  first overseas factory in brazil  claims of stock price manipulation  problems with police touring models   strike  mv agusta group  operations in india  financial crisis  motorcycle engines  big vtwins  small vtwins  revolution engine  düsseldorftest  singlecylinder engine